                "1": "Full customer management (add, edit, delete, and view list with advanced search and pagination)",
                "2": "User management including registration, editing, role changes, and deactivation",
                "3": "Define and edit slogans for printing on invoice footers",
                "4": "Product management with unit definition and pricing",
                "5": "Software subscription packages for purchase and management",
                "6": "Sales invoice system with product addition, discounts, payment, and returns",
